  "texts": [
    "The content encompasses intricate and multifaceted dialogues among multiple parties.",
    "• MultiNews (Fabbri et al, 2019).",
    "Derived from articles on news websites and summaries meticulously curated by seasoned editors, the MultiNews dataset boasts a diverse array of news sources, spanning across more than 1.5K unique sites.",
    "• Newsroom (Grusky et al, 2018).",
    "Constructed from 1.3M articles and their associated summaries, the Newsroom dataset is a compilation from 38 leading news publishers."
  ]
